README
------

Some of these demonstration scripts may require additional modules.


FILES
-----
named
 - Supposed to be a drop-in replacement for bind's /usr/sbin/named
 - (Conf file stuff not working yet.)

named.forwarder
 - Simple name server that forwards requests to another name server.
 - It keeps the time to live (TTL) of the responses in a cache.

named.dbmcache
 - Uses a dbmfile for the TTL cache.

mysql/README
 - Working example of SQL backend resolver.
 - Requires DBI and DBD::mysql to be installed.
